<title>USA: U.S. Global Investors names Clark CFO.</title>
<headline>U.S. Global Investors names Clark CFO.</headline>
<dateline>SAN ANTONIO, Texas 1997-05-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>U.S. Global Investors Inc said Monday it named David J. Clark chief financial officer.</p>
<p>The company said Clark was formerly a Foreign Service Officer for the United States Agency for International Development (USAID).</p>
<p>Clark replaces Robert Duncan, who will remain with the company as a consultant and member of the board of trustees, U.S. Global said.</p>
